Steps to run

1.Install the Arduino IDE in your PC and flah the code in the folder "NodeMCU-ESP8266- code"
2.create a account in IBM bluemix IOT and add te new device-NodeMcu
3.Import the code from the folder "Node-RED" in NODE-RED
4.Connect the relay to the nodeMcu and relay output to Inductionstove.
5.Please refer the schematic in "schematics" folder for hardware connection.
